{"history":[{"role":"user","content":"What aged care services are available?","timestamp":"2026-02-23T01:22:07.496Z"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Aged care services available through Services Australia include:\n\n1. **Support at Home**: This service provides assistance for older Australians who wish to remain living in their own homes. It includes various forms of support tailored to individual needs.\n\n2. **Residential Care**: This service is for older Australians who require a higher level of care and support, typically provided in a residential aged care facility.\n\n3. **Transition Care**: This program supports older Australians who are t","timestamp":"2026-02-23T01:22:07.496Z"}],"memories":[{"id":"mem-a82036b3-1771809727496","query":"What aged care services are available?","answer":"Aged care services available through Services Australia include:\n\n1. **Support at Home**: This service provides assistance for older Australians who wish to remain living in their own homes. It includes various forms of support tailored to individual needs.\n\n2. **Residential Care**: This service is for older Australians who require a higher level of care and support, typically provided in a residential aged care facility.\n\n3. **Transition Care**: This program supports older Australians who are transitioning from hospital to home or to a different care setting. It focuses on rehabilitation and recovery.\n\n4. **Short-term Restorative Care**: This service is designed to help older Australians regain their independence and improve their quality of life through short-term support.\n\n5. **Home Care Packages**: These packages provide a range of services to help older Australians live independently at home, including personal care, domestic assistance, and nursing care.\n\n6. **Continence Aids Payment Scheme**: This scheme assists individuals with incontinence by providing financial support for continence aids.\n\nFor more detailed information about these services, you can contact Services Australia or visit their website to explore specific eligibility criteria and application processes [Source 1][Source 5][Source 6].","sources":[{"file":"general/finding-other-help-when-youre-living-with-disability.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.28138984550566604},{"file":"general/software-for-aged-care-online-claiming.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.31770803197084063},{"file":"general/our-staff-can-help-you-with-your-aged-care-matters.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.34707868955605126},{"file":"general/set-up-aged-care-web-services-software.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.347273441031955},{"file":"general/transition-care-for-providers.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.3563955604544531},{"file":"general/most-useful-information-for-getting-aged-care-services.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.3756168889862021},{"file":"general/software-for-aged-care-online-claiming.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.3775527140403554},{"file":"general/using-aged-care-provider-portal.md","pageStart":1,"pageEnd":1,"score":0.38226889379833023}],"embedding":[0.0064289080910384655,-0.018839634954929352,-0.001003400655463338,0.04603429511189461,-0.07296145707368851,0.08407945185899734,-0.04891553893685341,-0.0494590662419796,-0.055555667728185654,-0.0507749542593956,0.03353974595665932,0.025709088891744614,0.008032349869608879,0.05107893794775009,0.024472365155816078,-0.07382041960954666,-0.05390544608235359,-0.015896940603852272,0.02846447564661503,-0.04906248301267624,-0.019026752561330795,0.08433672785758972,-0.049840204417705536,0.003753915661945939,-0.007665054872632027,-0.004496674053370953,-0.103363536298275,-0.07498824596405029,0.05155821517109871,0.020538531243801117,0.06957588344812393,0.019140681251883507,-0.015271062031388283,-0.023064730688929558,-0.023524368181824684,0.054797541350126266,0.02239859662950039,0.02582959085702896,-0.10972295701503754,0.03560466319322586,-0.023884478956460953,-0.03854728862643242,-0.03886